///  Р­С‚Рѕ РѕРїРёСЃР°РЅРёРµ РєР»Р°СЃСЃР° Р°РІС‚РѕРјР°С‚РёС‡РµСЃРєРё СЃРіРµРЅРµСЂРµРЅРѕ РёР· С„Р°Р№Р» L:\_ZD\txt\ExtEnv.txt
 Class ASUOOAm.ExtEnv Extends %Persistent
{


 /// NPP;1;1;;
Property NPP As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ENV_TYPE;2;1;;
Property ENVTYPE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ENVSUBTYPE;3;1;;
Property ENVSUBTYPE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// NUMBER;4;1;;
Property NUMBER As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// MADEBY;5;1;;
Property MADEBY As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// DETAILS;6;1;;
Property DETAILS As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// REL_YEAR;7;1;;
Property REL_YEAR As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// SALER;8;1;;
Property SALER As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// COMP;9;1;;
Property COMP As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);


/// РРјРїРѕСЂС‚ РґР°РЅРЅС‹С… РёР· С‚РµРєСЃС‚РѕРІРѕРіРѕ С„Р°Р№Р»Р° L:\_ZD\txt\ExtEnv.txt
/// W ##CLASS(ASUOOAm.ExtEnv).Import("")
ClassMethod Import(fn as %String) As %String
{
 if $g(fn)="" s fn="L:\_ZD\txt\ExtEnv.txt"
 s sc=##class(ASUOOAm.ExtEnv).%KillExtent()
 i 'sc w sc q
 D File2Arr^%ZAPM.bs.BSCEXE(fn,.fT1),STR2MAS^%ZAPM.bs.BSCmail(.fT1,.fT2,$C(13,10)) K fT1 s S1=$$s1^%ZAPM.bs.BSre(0),S2=$$s2^%ZAPM.bs.BSre(0)
 S i="" F i2=1:1 S i=$O(fT2(i)) Q:i=""  I i2>1 s m=$G(fT2(i)) d  w i2_" " 
 .s ii="" F i1=1:1 q:$p(m,"@",i1,i1+1)=""  s da=$tr($p(m,"@",i1),S1,S2) d  S ii=ii_da_"," 
 .s ii=$e(ii,1,$l(ii)-1)
 .x "i ##class(ASUOOAm.ExtEnvEdit).Add("_ii_")" 
 q 1
}
}

