///  Р­С‚Рѕ РѕРїРёСЃР°РЅРёРµ РєР»Р°СЃСЃР° Р°РІС‚РѕРјР°С‚РёС‡РµСЃРєРё СЃРіРµРЅРµСЂРµРЅРѕ РёР· С„Р°Р№Р» L:\_ZD\txt\comps.txt
 Class ASUOOAm.comps Extends %Persistent
{


 /// NPP;1;1;;
Property NPP As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// NUMER;2;1;;
Property NUMER As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// INDATE;3;1;date;
Property INDATE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// OUTYEAR;4;1;;
Property OUTYEAR As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// MADEBY;5;1;;
Property MADEBY As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// WARRANTY;6;1;;
Property WARRANTY As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// SALER;7;1;;
Property SALER As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// WHOTAKE;8;1;;
Property WHOTAKE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// DEPART;9;1;;
Property DEPART As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// HOUSE;10;1;;
Property HOUSE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ROOM;11;1;;
Property ROOM As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// COMPTYPE;12;1;;
Property COMPTYPE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// FECARDNUM;13;1;;
Property FECARDNUM As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// MTCARDNUM;14;1;;
Property MTCARDNUM As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ISWHOLE;15;1;;
Property ISWHOLE As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// SUPPORT;16;1;;
Property SUPPORT As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// SOCKETS;17;1;;
Property SOCKETS As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// EXTUNITS;18;1;;
Property EXTUNITS As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// OS;19;1;;
Property OS As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// PROGS;20;1;;
Property PROGS As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ISASPP;21;1;;
Property ISASPP As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ISREM;22;1;;
Property ISREM As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// ISENV;23;1;;
Property ISENV As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);

 /// F;24;1;;
Property F As %String(MAXLEN = 1000);


/// РРјРїРѕСЂС‚ РґР°РЅРЅС‹С… РёР· С‚РµРєСЃС‚РѕРІРѕРіРѕ С„Р°Р№Р»Р° L:\_ZD\txt\comps.txt
/// W ##CLASS(ASUOOAm.comps).Import("")
ClassMethod Import(fn as %String) As %String
{
 if $g(fn)="" s fn="L:\_ZD\txt\comps.txt"
 s sc=##class(ASUOOAm.comps).%KillExtent()
 i 'sc w sc q
 D File2Arr^%ZAPM.bs.BSCEXE(fn,.fT1),STR2MAS^%ZAPM.bs.BSCmail(.fT1,.fT2,$C(13,10)) K fT1 s S1=$$s1^%ZAPM.bs.BSre(0),S2=$$s2^%ZAPM.bs.BSre(0)
 S i="" F i2=1:1 S i=$O(fT2(i)) Q:i=""  I i2>1 s m=$G(fT2(i)) d  w i2_" " 
 .s ii="" F i1=1:1 q:$p(m,"@",i1,i1+1)=""  s da=$tr($p(m,"@",i1),S1,S2) d  S ii=ii_da_"," 
 ..i i1=3 s da=$c(34)_$p(da,".",3)_"-"_$p(da,".",2)_" "_$p(da,".",1)_$c(34)
 .s ii=$e(ii,1,$l(ii)-1)
 .x "i ##class(ASUOOAm.compsEdit).Add("_ii_")" 
 q 1
}
}

